Dataset Notice:

The M3 Competition data included in the data/ directory originates from
the Mcomp R package (https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/Mcomp/),
authored by Rob Hyndman, Muhammad Akram, Christoph Bergmeir, and
Mitchell O'Hara-Wild, and licensed under GPL-3. The original dataset is
described in:

  Makridakis, S., & Hibon, M. (2000). The M3-Competition: Results,
  Conclusions and Implications. International Journal of Forecasting,
  16(4), 451-476.
